**These are the list of UI/features**

We will have 3 users, (Corp member, accommodation agent and Admin).
The Corp member registers with all his necessary details including state of deployment and lga posted to.
The Corp member too will have the ability to search for accommodation by state or local govt.
The Agent in charge of accomodation will register with all necessary details that can only upload vacant accommodation up for rent with location too.
The admin oversees everything on the platform.
You can only register as a Corp member or as an agent
Corp member can see all available accommodation and it's individual details including agent's contact details so he/she can place a call through to show interest in securing the house and negotiations.
Verifiable Agent directory for security reasons for corpers safety
Sale zone for any corper passing out wishing to sell his or her things to incoming corp member.
